                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-913" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES SPRINGETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the brother of John Springett—I was present when the prisoner was in front of the bar—I saw him <hi rend="italic">chuck</hi> down a shilling—I picked it up, and gave it into his own hand—as soon as he saw the police<lb></lb>man come in he let it drop between his legs—I took it up, marked it, and gave it to my brother.</p>
